high_descs: Turn around then turn left and face the counter by the stove in front of you.
Take the silver knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the counter on your right.
Slice the tomato on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter in front of you.
Take a tomato slice off of the counter in front of you.
Turn right and face the microwave on top of the stove to your left.
Heat up the tomato slice in the microwave and take it out.
Turn around and face the sink in front of you.
Place the warm tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm tomato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left to walk around the kitchen island, hanging a left and stopping at the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the smaller knife on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn to face the tomato on the counter.
Slice the tomato with the smaller knife.
Turn around to face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn around to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the countertop.
Turn right and walk to the microwave.
Heat up the slice of tomato in the microwave, removing it afterwards.
Turn left to walk back to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a tomato slice in the microwave to put in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the counter on the left side of stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Look to the left to face the tomato on the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Turn around to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato on the counter.
Take a step to the right to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and step forward to face the sink.
Place the tomato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato slice and place it in the sink.
